        <li class="blue">Avoid substantial radiation as much as possible</li>
        <li class="blue">Avoid smoking, smoking environment and alcohol</li>
        <li class="blue">Avoid chemicals/toxins either by inhalation or through the mouth or skin as much as possible
        </li>
        <li class="blue">Avoid unnecessary exposure to ultraviolet radiation(sun and artificial sources)</li>
